snippet.title: Amber Heard Faked Her Pregnancy For Publicity?
snippet.description:
On July 1, Heard disclosed that she had secretly welcomed a baby daughter called Oonagh Paige via surrogacy in an Instagram post. “I'm overjoyed to be able to share this news with you. I made the decision to have a child four years ago." She wrote, "I wanted to do it on my own terms." “I realize now how revolutionary it is for us as women to consider one of the most fundamental aspects of our lives in this way.
